  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Place the Brie in a baking dish and drizzle with olive oil, honey, lemon juice, and cracked pepper.",
    "Sprinkle smoked paprika and berbere spice mix over the cheese.",
    "Cover with foil and bake for 10 minutes.",
    "Remove foil and bake another 5 minutes until the top is golden and the cheese is bubbling.",
    "Serve the hot Brie with toasted flatbread slices for dipping."
